title: Billerica North, moderate size, one person
posting_body: ['Billerica North - One mile from train station.', '*IF YOU’RE SEEING THIS AD, THEN IT’S STILL FOR RENT*', 'Moderate sized Apt. on 1st Fl.', 'Owner Occupied.', 'In 100+ yr.', 'old 2-family.', 'Owner Occ.', 'For One quiet person.', 'Wood floors, NO Pets, NO Smoking/Vaping,', 'NO Handymen/Painting.', 'NO Exceptions!', 'No Laundry Avail. & Tenant Shovels own snow.', '4 Rm.', 'One Bedroom, Bath, Living & Kitchenette.', 'Some basement storage.', 'Place for One car parking - off street.', 'NO open house.', 'RESPONSES MUST INCLUDE YOUR PHONE NUMBER & NAME.', 'Thanks.', '*(I do Not respond to "Is This  Still Available?")', '(this is Sm.', 'but perfect for One person who is quiet.', "Tried 2 and it didn't work.", "Hasn't been rented in some time, still getting organized.", "This probably won't be a quick process.", 'Trying to save Everyone time (including myself) by being upfront.', 'Seeking someone to rent Long-term.', "Please be patient and don't flood me with emails.", "I'm sure I'll be swamped anyways.", 'Exact date avail.', 'Undetermined)', '$1,375 Per Mo.', 'Plus (you pay) Utilities.']
